  "section_name": "Investment Recommendation & Outlook",
  "text": "Based on the comprehensive analysis of American Express Company's financial performance, competitive positioning, and risk profile, we assign a Hold rating to AXP shares as of November 12, 2025. The company has demonstrated solid operational execution with Q3 2025 revenue reaching $10.42 billion and net income of $2.90 billion, representing year-over-year growth of 0.91% and 0.59% respectively. Net margin expansion to 27.86% from 25.80% in the prior-year quarter reflects improving profitability trends throughout 2025.",
